<lb n="0466c17"/>那<note place="inline">引</note>莫<note place="inline">三</note>拽寫拽他<note place="inline">引</note>那<note place="inline">引</note>莫帝<note place="inline">引</note>那<note place="inline">四</note>怛吐<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0466c18"/>佐<note place="inline">引</note>囉曳<note n="0466004" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">&CB00819;＝怛【三】</note><note n="0466004" resp="CBETA" type="mod"><app><lem resp="CBETA.Maha">&CB02487;</lem><rdg wit="【大】">&CB00819;</rdg></app>＝怛【宋】【元】【明】</note><app n="0466004"><lem>&CB02487;</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】" resp="Taisho">怛</rdg></app>咩<note place="inline">五</note></p>
<lb n="0466c19"/><p>受灌頂已。然可得受諸佛成就大金剛杵。復
<lb n="0466c20"/>次頌曰</p>
<lb n="0466c21"/><lg><l>汝常持此金剛杵</l><l>即金剛手堅固戒</l>
<lb n="0466c22"/><l>金剛薩埵勝修中</l><l>一切由斯得成佛</l></lg>
<lb n="0466c23"/><p>復次大明曰</p>
