<lb n="0466c25"/>囉<note place="inline"><note n="0466005" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二＝一【三】【宮】</note><note n="0466005" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二＝一【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note><app n="0466005"><lem>二</lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【明】【宮】" resp="Taisho">一</rdg></app>合</note>三摩曳<note place="inline">引</note>底瑟&CB00109;<note n="0466006" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">二合二＝一合【宋】【元】【宮】，二合【明】</note><note n="0466006" resp="CBETA" type="mod">二合二＝一合【宋】【元】【宮】，＝二合【明】</note><app n="0466006"><lem><note place="inline">二合</note><note place="inline">二</note></lem><rdg wit="【宋】【元】【宮】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">一合</note></rdg><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho"><note place="inline">二合</note></rdg></app>伊沙埵<note place="inline">引</note>馱<note place="inline">引</note>
<lb n="0466c26"/>囉夜<note place="inline"><note n="0466007" resp="Taisho" type="orig" place="foot text">引＋（二）【明】</note><app n="0466007"><lem>引</lem><rdg wit="【明】" resp="Taisho">引二</rdg></app></note>彌&CB00085;日囉<note place="inline">二合</note>薩埵<note place="inline">三</note>呬呬呬呬吽<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">四</note></p>
<lb n="0466c27"/><p>然後從普賢心安布大印三昧。隨說如是心
<lb n="0466c28"/>大明曰</p>
<lb n="0466c29"/><p type="dharani">摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>三摩<app type="＊" source="0465002"><lem>邪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">耶</rdg></app>薩埵三摩<app type="＊" source="0465002"><lem>邪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">耶</rdg></app>薩怛&CB00680;<note place="inline">三合一<app type="＊" source="0465003"><lem>句</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【明】">&lac;</rdg></app></note>摩
<pb ed="T" id="T18.0884.0467a" n="0467a"/>
<lb n="0467a01"/>賀<note place="inline">引</note>三摩<app type="＊" source="0465002"><lem>邪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">耶</rdg></app>薩都<note place="inline">引</note>&CB00780;<note place="inline">二</note>摩賀<note place="inline">引</note>三摩<app type="＊" source="0465002"><lem>邪</lem><rdg resp="Taisho" wit="【宋】【元】【明】">耶</rdg></app>薩
<lb n="0467a02"/>埵<note place="inline">引</note>提底瑟&CB00109;<note place="inline">二合</note>莎&CB00805;<note place="inline">引</note><note place="inline">三</note></p>
<lb n="0467a03"/><p>如是印明。執金剛等諸菩薩眾。皆悉於彼諸
<lb n="0467a04"/>印真實大三昧中同一成就</p>
<lb n="0467a05"/><p>復次身語心金剛所成心大明曰</p>
